data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome to Enclave at Prestancia, a prestigious gated community located in the heart of Palmer Ranch. This inviting two-story home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, plus a dedicated office, all within its spacious 3,204 sq ft layout. In 2022, the home was updated  aiming at enhancing comfort and peace of mind, including a new roof, upgraded windows, a new HVAC system, and plush carpeting. Upon entering the foyer, you're greeted by graceful columns leading to the dining room, while to the left, a formal living room awaits, featuring a gas fireplace, large windows, and French doors opening to the courtyard. As you make your way through, you'll discover an office with a built-in desk and shelving and a conveniently placed half bath, seamlessly leading you to the inviting kitchen. A chef’s delight, the kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, tasteful backsplash, and ample cabinet and counter space. Overlooking the breakfast area and family room, it provides a seamless flow for both daily living and entertaining. The breakfast area showcases high ceilings, a dry bar, and a unique skylight window, bathing the space in natural light. High ceilings continue as you step down into the family room, perfect for movie nights or hosting guests, with access to a multi-season lanai offering views of the 10th green of the Stadium course. The primary suite on the first level provides a peaceful retreat with ample natural light, access to the lanai, generous closet space, and a luxurious ensuite bath featuring dual vanities, a jetted tub, walk-in shower, and a private door leading to the courtyard oasis. Outside, in the private screened-in courtyard, find a refreshing soaker pool with an elegant fountain, complemented by a covered area featuring an outdoor kitchen ideal for crafting meals and dining by the poolside. Upstairs, two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom await, with one bedroom offering dual closets, a built-in vanity, and ensuite access, while the other boasts a walk-in closet and views of the golf course. Enclave at Prestancia offers residents a lifestyle of leisure and luxury with maintenance-free living, proximity to Siesta Key Beach, world-class golf facilities, social activities, a full-service restaurant and bar, and a recently renovated clubhouse with optional membership. With 24-hour manned entrances and convenient access to beaches, shopping, dining, and entertainment, Prestancia invites you to embrace the Sarasota lifestyle. This home is currently financed with an assumable VA Loan.
